gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 117, Raptors 94
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Raptors, 117-94. Jaylen Brown led all scorers with 29 points (12-20 FG) and five rebounds for the Celtics, while Jayson Tatum added 27 points, five rebounds and four assists in the victory. Pascal Siakam tallied 17 points, seven rebounds and three assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Celtics improve to 7-2 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 4-5.
